CardPay,s,Payment,API,is,a,payment,management,platform,where,users,can,receive,payments,and,check,payment,statuses,The,API,can,operate,via,directing,customers,to,CardPay,s,Payment,Page,or,to,a,merchants,External,Payment,Page,Both,methods,are,managed,and,verified,by,CardPay,CardPay,is,PCI,DSS,certified,and,compliant,and,all,connections,are,secured,through,Thawte,DV,SSL,certificates